Direct Known Subclasses:
ColumnMap, Table
public class IndexedHashMap<K,V>
extends java.util.ArrayList<java.util.Map.Entry<K,V>>

IndexedHashMap is a hybrid class. Publically, it is an arraylist of Entries. The difference is that it has some hash map capabilites, due to it's private map.
